  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_3",
    "text": "11111 铁路 国界 山山峰",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.2547652254765225,
      0.2836459361632116,
      0.7280334728033473,
      0.3323461665021389
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_4",
    "text": "2.地形图的判读",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09205020920502092,
      0.37643961829549194,
      0.26778242677824265,
      0.397499177360974
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_5",
    "text": "(1)地面高度的计算方法",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12366341236634124,
      0.40802895689371504,
      0.37563923756392376,
      0.4297466271799934
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_6",
    "text": "①海拔(绝对高度)：地面某个地点高出海平面的垂直距离。 举例：珠穆朗玛峰海拔8844.43米，吐鲁番盆地海拔一155米 ②相对高度：某个地点高出另一地点的垂直距离.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1487680148768015,
      0.43566962816716026,
      0.795908879590888,
      0.5297795327410333
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_7",
    "text": "举例：旗杆高出地面15米",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.17666201766620176,
      0.5317538664034221,
      0.4351464435146444,
      0.5534715366897005
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_8",
    "text": "(2)地形图的类型：等高线地形图、分层设色地形图、地形图剖面图。 等高线：在地图上把海拨相同的各点连成的线。 等深线：在地图上把海洋中深度相同的各点连接成线。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12273361227336123,
      0.5633432050016453,
      0.7549976754997676,
      0.6482395524843698
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_9",
    "text": "(3)等高线地形图的判读.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12087401208740121,
      0.6561368871339256,
      0.3682008368200837,
      0.6791707798617966
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_10",
    "text": "①根据等高线的疏完程度判断坡度的陡缓：高线稀疏，表示坡缓：等高线 集表示坡陡。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08926080892608089,
      0.6877262257321487,
      0.9335192933519293,
      0.7403751233958539
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_11",
    "text": "②根据等高线形状判断地形类型：山顶、山背、山谷、鞍部、陡崖。等高线的弯曲 部分向高处凸出表示山谷，向低处凸出表示山背：两个山顶之间的部位是鞍部；等高线重叠 的地方表示陡崖。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08740120874012088,
      0.7502467917077986,
      0.9363086936308693,
      0.8351431391905232
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10_12",
    "text": "(4)陆地上的五种基本地形：平原、高原、山地，丘陵、盆地。地形图上用海拔来表示地面的 高低起伏。分层设色形图上，绿色表示平原，蓝色表示海洋、黄色表示高山高原、白色表示冰川。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.08182240818224082,
      0.8423823626192827,
      0.9437470943747094,
      0.9305692662059888
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_10",
    "order": 13
  }
]